      <main class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds" role="main" id="main">
        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Connect to GovWifi using an Android device</h1>
        <p class="govuk-body">Once you have a GovWifi <%= link_to "username and password", "/connect-to-govwifi", class: "govuk-link" %>, follow the steps below.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Different Android devices can vary. If your device does not show exactly what is explained here, select the closest option or contact your IT support desk for help.</p>

        <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">Open your wifi settings. A list of wifi networks will appear.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">Select <strong>GovWifi</strong>. A settings menu will appear.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>EAP method</strong>, select <strong>PEAP</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>Phase 2 authentication</strong>, select <strong>MSCHAPV2</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>CA Certificate</strong>, select <strong>Use system certificates</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>Domain</strong>, enter wifi.service.gov.uk</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>Identity</strong>, enter the GovWifi username you received by email or text.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">Leave <strong>Anonymous identity</strong> blank.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">For <strong>Password</strong>, enter the GovWifi password you received by email or text. Your password is case sensitive. It's 3 words without spaces. The first letter of each word is capitalised.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p class="govuk-body">Select <strong>Connect</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="govuk-body">You should now be connected to GovWifi.</p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Support</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">If you're having problems, contact IT support for the building you're in.</p>
      </main>
